Create my first chart!

Visual data for density point

set.seed(42)
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point() 

ggplot(diamonds %>% sample_n(50), aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point()

Create my second chart! - smooth line

Visual data for trend carat and price

set.seed(42)
ggplot(diamonds %>% sample_n(5000), aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth()

Create my 4 chart! - ggplot mapping

set.seed(42)
ggplot(diamonds %>% sample_n(500),
       mapping = aes(carat, price, col=cut)) +
  geom_point(size=5, alpha=0.9)

Create my 4 chart! - ggplot gradient

ggplot(mtcars, mapping=aes(hp, mpg, col=wt)) +
  geom_point(size=5, alpha=0.7) +
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_color_gradient(low="gold", high = "red")

Create my 5 chart! - ggplot facet_wrap

set.seed(42)
ggplot(diamonds %>% sample_n(5000), aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point(alpha=0.5) + 
  theme_minimal() +
  geom_smooth(col="red", fill="yellow") +
  facet_wrap( ~cut, ncol=3)
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'gam' and formula = 'y ~ s(x, bs = "cs")'
